data.description: Welcome home to this charming 3 bed / 2bath bungalow in Community Heights near Ellenberger Park. Featuring original hardwood floors throughout the main level, a wood-burning limestone fireplace, a1 car garage, a full-sized basketball court, a partially fenced in backyard, and a fully enclosed front porch for enjoying your morning coffee. This home has much to love!! Enjoy the newly updated kitchen with granite countertops, new kitchen  sink and faucet, freshly painted cabinets and an adjoining breakfast nook.  Additionally, there is a full, updated bath on the main level and 2 bedrooms with large closets. There is another full bath & master bdrm in the basement. The roof, exterior paint, interior paint and sump pump were installed in 2021.
